---
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8" />
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
<title>Calibi Sync — Your rhythm. Your wellness. In sync.</title>
<meta name="description" content="Track your cycle, workouts, and energy with Calibi Sync — your all-in-one wellness rhythm guide." />
<meta name="theme-color" content="#F4C8C2" />
<link rel="icon" href="/favicon.ico" />
<!-- Fonts -->
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@400;600;700&family=Playfair+Display:wght@700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
<style>
:root {
--bg:#FFF7F4;
--pink:#F4C8C2;
--willow:#A3C4A8;
--brown:#4B3F36;
--brown2:#6B5C4F;
--radius:16px;
}
html,body{margin:0;padding:0;background:var(--bg);color:var(--brown);
font-family:'Poppins',system-ui,sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:1.6;}
h1,h2,h3{font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;line-height:1.2;margin:0;}
a{text-decoration:none;color:var(--brown);}
.container{max-width:1120px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 20px;}
.section{padding:64px 0;}
.btn{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;padding:12px 18px;
border-radius:12px;font-weight:600;border:1px solid transparent;transition:.15s ease-in-out;}
.btn-primary{background:var(--willow);color:#fff;}
.btn-primary:hover{opacity:.9;}
.btn-secondary{background:var(--pink);color:var(--brown);}
.btn-secondary:hover{filter:brightness(.98);}
.card{background:#fff;border:1px solid color-mix(in oklab,var(--willow)25%,transparent);
border-radius:var(--radius);padding:24px;box-shadow:0 8px 24px rgba(0,0,0,.04);}
.grid{display:grid;gap:16px;}
.grid-2{grid-template-columns:1fr;}
@media(min-width:768px){.grid-2{grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr);}}
.footer{padding:28px 0;background:#fff;border-top:1px solid color-mix(in oklab,var(--willow)25%,transparent);}
.footer a:hover{text-decoration:underline;}
.hero-img{width:100%;max-width:520px;border-radius:24px;box-shadow:0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,.06);}
.tag{display:inline-block;padding:6px 10px;background:var(--pink);color:var(--brown);
border-radius:999px;font-weight:600;font-size:14px;}
#privacy,#terms{padding:64px 0;background:#fff;}
#privacy h1,#terms h1{font-size:32px;margin-bottom:12px;}
#privacy p,#terms p,#privacy li,#terms li{line-height:1.7;color:var(--brown2);}
</style>
</head>

<body>
<!-- HEADER -->
<header class="container" style="padding:18px 0;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;">
<a href="#top" style="display:flex;gap:10px;align-items:center;">
<img src="/images/logo.svg" alt="Calibi Sync" width="32" height="32" />
<strong>Calibi Sync</strong>
</a>
<nav style="display:flex;gap:18px;">
<a href="#features">Features</a>
<a href="#pricing">Pricing</a>
<a href="#privacy">Privacy</a>
<a href="#terms">Terms</a>
</nav>
</header>

<!-- HERO -->
<section id="top" class="section">
<div class="container" style="display:grid;gap:28px;align-items:center;">
<div>
<span class="tag">New • Live Workout Mode</span>
<h1 style="font-size:48px;margin-top:12px;">Your rhythm. Your wellness. In sync.</h1>
<p style="margin-top:10px;color:var(--brown2);max-width:52ch;">
Track your cycle, workouts, and energy with Calibi Sync — your all-in-one wellness rhythm guide.
</p>
<div style="display:flex;gap:12px;margin-top:18px;flex-wrap:wrap;">
<a class="btn btn-primary" href="#download">Get the App</a>
<a class="btn btn-secondary" href="#waitlist">Join the Waitlist</a>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<img class="hero-img" src="/images/iphone-mock.png" alt="Calibi Sync app" />
</div>
</div>
</section>

<!-- FEATURES -->
<section id="features" class="section" style="background:#fff;">
<div class="container">
<h2 style="font-size:36px;">Designed to sync with you</h2>
<div class="grid grid-2" style="margin-top:22px;">
<div class="card"><h3>Cycle Tracking</h3><p>Know your phases and plan with confidence.</p></div>
<div class="card"><h3>Live Workout Mode</h3><p>Track sets, reps, weight and rest timers.</p></div>
<div class="card"><h3>Progress Gallery</h3><p>Private photos with Face ID + privacy mode.</p></div>
<div class="card"><h3>Journaling</h3><p>Reflect, release, and reset with daily prompts.</p></div>
</div>
</div>
</section>

<!-- PRICING -->
<section id="pricing" class="section">
<div class="container" style="text-align:center;">
<h2 style="font-size:36px;">Membership</h2>
<p style="color:var(--brown2);margin-top:6px;">Start free • Upgrade for deeper insights</p>
<div class="grid grid-2" style="margin-top:24px;">
<div class="card">
<h3>Free</h3>
<ul><li>• Cycle calendar + basic logs</li><li>• Notes & reminders</li></ul>
</div>
<div class="card" style="border-color:var(--willow);">
<h3>Premium</h3>
<p style="color:var(--brown2);">$14.99 / mo or $119.99 / yr</p>
<ul>
<li>• Live Workout Mode</li>
<li>• Progress Gallery + Face ID</li>
<li>• Journaling & Insights</li>
</ul>
<a class="btn btn-primary" href="#download" style="margin-top:12px;">Start Syncing</a>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>

<!-- WAITLIST CTA -->
<section id="waitlist" class="section" style="background:var(--pink);">
<div class="container" style="display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;gap:16px;flex-wrap:wrap;">
<div>
<h2 style="font-size:32px;">Be first to know when we launch</h2>
<p style="color:var(--brown);">Join the waitlist and get early access.</p>
</div>
<form name="waitlist" method="POST" data-netlify="true" class="card"
style="display:flex;gap:10px;background:#fff;">
<input type="hidden" name="form-name" value="waitlist" />
<input name="email" type="email" required placeholder="Enter your email"
style="padding:12px 14px;border:1px solid #ddd;border-radius:10px;min-width:240px;">
<button class="btn btn-primary" type="submit">Join</button>
</form>
</div>
</section>

<!-- PRIVACY POLICY -->
<section id="privacy">
<div class="container card">
<h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
<p><strong>Effective:</strong> October 2025</p>
<p>Calibi Sync LLC (“Calibi Sync,” “we,” “us”) operates the Calibi Sync mobile app and website. This policy explains what we collect, how we use it, and your choices.</p>
<h2>Information We Collect</h2>
<ul>
<li>Account info (email, password, preferences).</li>
<li>Wellness logs (cycle dates, workouts, notes).</li>
<li>Photos (optional, private storage).</li>
<li>Device/usage analytics and subscription status.</li>
</ul>
<h2>How We Use Data</h2>
<p>To provide app features, maintain accounts, and improve performance. We never sell data.</p>
<h2>Deletion</h2>
<p>When you delete your account, all data is permanently deleted from active systems immediately, and removed from encrypted backups through rotation.</p>
<h2>Contact</h2>
<p>Email: <a href="mailto:privacy@calibisync.com">privacy@calibisync.com</a></p>
</div>
</section>

<!-- TERMS OF SERVICE -->
<section id="terms">
<div class="container card">
<h1>Terms of Service</h1>
<p><strong>Effective:</strong> October 2025</p>
<h2>Acceptance</h2>
<p>By using Calibi Sync, you agree to these Terms and our Privacy Policy.</p>
<h2>Health Disclaimer</h2>
<p>Calibi Sync provides wellness tracking and insights for informational purposes only. It is not a substitute for medical advice.</p>
<h2>Billing</h2>
<p>Premium features are handled through Apple/Google billing via RevenueCat. Cancel anytime through your app store account.</p>
<h2>Account Deletion</h2>
<p>You may delete your account anytime. Data is removed from our systems immediately and securely.</p>
<h2>Contact</h2>
<p>Email: <a href="mailto:support@calibisync.com">support@calibisync.com</a></p>
</div>
</section>

<!-- FOOTER -->
<footer class="footer">
<div class="container" style="display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:12px;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;">
<span>© {year} Calibi Sync</span>
<nav style="display:flex;gap:16px;">
<a href="#privacy">Privacy</a>
<a href="#terms">Terms</a>
<a href="#waitlist">Contact</a>
</nav>
</div>
</footer>
</body>
</html>
